channel.title: Astral Projection,Does it Exist?
channel.description:
I saw a topic about this sometime in November,and i did some studying about it.I think astral projection is sum what real due to the fact when you sleep you dream and it feels like an eternity in your sleep sometimes.Heres some information i got off the google
[url=http://paranormal.about.com/library/weekly/aa110501a.htm]http://paranormal.about.com/library/weekly/aa110501a.htm[/url] - Astral Projection:You Can Do It Too [url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astral_projection]http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Astral_projection[/url] -Astral projection -wikipedia
Astral Project is a out of body experince that has atleast happends once in everyones life as a near death experience or when they were a child.Astral project is said to be leaving your body while you sleep or at rest and going anywhere your spirit/mind takes you.They say theres no time,so if you want to go somewhere your instantly there.
So please vote and tell me what you think about the topic
